    "description": "<div class=\"stackedit__html\"><p>When you take damage, hit using a melee weapon, or succeed on a Check (excluding Accuracy Checks) that relies on Might or Willpower, you gain 1 Hype. You also gain <strong>【SL + 1】</strong>. Hype when you invoke your Traits or Bonds. You lose half your current Hype when you rest (to a minimum of 1). </p><p>You may use an action to perform a finisher with your choice of flairs (found further in this document), spending as much Hype as you have. Each time you acquire this Skill, learn 2 flairs.</p></div>",
